snippet.textDisplay:
I just wanted to mention that I understand how unrelentingly soul sucking youtube can be. Which has to be profoundly exacerbated by the fact that you put such an extreme amount of effort and care into all of your videos. you are a rare example of someone who actually succeeds at beating the youtube algorythm, and it's demands of a constant stream of content. I do hope that you are still getting the support from the platform that other creators who focus on quantity over quality benefit from...

that being said, if you ever need help getting anything done, you do have a devoted following of VFX nerds who want to lend a hand (myself included), maybe opening yourself up to a little more help, might make the process a little less of a slog?


anyway, I love your work, and am STOKED whenever you get around to releasing one of your masterpieces. I hope you never feel like you have to rush to keep up with your audiences expectations.
